Subject: [PATCH 4.19 18/89] r8152: check disconnect status after long sleep
Date:   Tue, 17 Mar 2020 11:54:27 +0100
Message-Id: <20200317103302.102954540@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.1
